		   <table class="mform"  border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
		   <tr><td class="headerrow" colspan="2" class="mform" valign="top">Guide 1-60 for an Erudite Shadowknight<br clear=all>
		   <span class="sm">Posted @ Sat, Dec 23rd 4:58 PM2000 </span><span id="notbold">| <span class=sm>IP: Logged</span> | <a href="/db/classes.html?class=5&mid=9775906844789&post=1"><a class=sm href="/db/classes.html?class=5&mid=9775906844789&num=0&post=1&replyto=9775906844789"><img src=/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=11 width=17> Reply to this</a></a>    <a name=9775906844789></a></small></td></tr>
		   <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform" ><span id="notbold">By:</span> <span id=>Anonymous</span></a><b><span id=></span></b>
		   <br><nobr><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default [2.00]</nobr><br><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=Anonymous&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>First off, this is by no means what anyone else will tell you, simply my opinion.<br><br>Level's 1-5<br><br>Start out in Paineel, your home city, the newbie zone is pretty much empty and nothing is really aggro.&nbsp;&nbsp;At about 4, if you see Noclin's pet, kill him and give his remains to Noclin.  When you hit 5, follow the left wall to the water, then follow the water to a bridge, then follow the right wall to Erudin.  STAY AWAY FROM THE PALADINS AND CLERIC'S and you should be alright.  Jump off the boat before it docks or get an invis and get to the town gate, get bound.<br><br>Lvl's 6-12<br><br>These can be spent in the upper and middle floor's of Blackburrow killing any gnoll's you can handle, don't group.  At 9 go get your spells.  Keep killing gnolls until you are at least 1 bubble into 12, then head over to Freeport.  Get bound at the docks.<br><br>Lvl's 13-16<br><br>These can be spent killing the sisters of sister Isle in OOT, be sure to jump off the boat before it docks, loot ALL the belts for money.  If you use a pet, make sure it DOESN'T follow you but guards one place.  To leave you will need a teleport, but you should have enough money by now to pay if they so desire.<br><br>Lvl 17-22<br><br>Time to go back to Qeynos and to East Karana for Gnoll Reavers and Undead Gnoll Reaver's, you will have to group at first and take them, but around 20, you should be able to solo them pretty easily through 22, at which time you should go get your spells.<br><br>Lvl's 23-33<br><br>Time to head to Cazic Thule and kill Maze trash until 27 or 28, then get in a Pyramid group and ask politely to have all the decayed armor (unless there is another SK in the group who needs it, in which case you will have to roll.)<br><br>Lvl's 34-42<br><br>You should have all of your Darkforge by now, and a decent weapon, so it's back to Sister Isle for dwarves solo, kill them until about 39, then you should head to the western commonlands and kill Valon and Colin guards by the tollbooth. Do this until 42<br><br>Lvl's 43-50<br><br>These should be spent grouping in lower guk, killing just about anything really.  At 50, there are many ways you can go but Wurm's in skyfire should prove sufficient for a while.<br><br>I will not spoil everything so 55+ are your's to figure out, you should be experience enough by now to figure out where to go, but Chardok, and Sebelis are a few hints.<br><br>GOOD LUCK!  </p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >0 Replies</td></tr></table></td></tr></table><tr><td class=mhback align=right><span class=mh id=fs8><a class=mh href=/db/classes.html?class=5><img src=/shared/root_thread_ico.gif border=0 alt="Up" width=17 height=11> Thread Index</a> |  <a class=mh href=/db/classes.html?class=5&post=1><img src=/shared/new_thread_ico.gif border=0 alt="New" width=17 height=11> New Subject</a> | <a class=mh href=/db/classes.html?class=5&mid=9775906844789&num=0&post=1&mid=9775906844789><img src=/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif border=0 alt="Reply" width=17 height=11> Reply to Thread</a></span></td></tr><tr><td><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="mform"><tr><td id="fs8">0 Posts [ <a href="/fsearch.html?base=class5">Search Forums</a> ]</nobr></td></tr></table>&nbsp;</td></tr>
